text: Annie Ros (5 March 1926 - 14 June 2013) was a Dutch gymnast. She competed at the 1948 Summer Olympics and the 1952 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1926 births Category:2013 deaths Category:Dutch female artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of the Netherlands Category:Gymnasts at the 1948 Summer Olympics Category:Gymnasts at the 1952 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Utrecht (city)
